* Configure Shares\n& Recipients
** CREATE SHARE
***_ Container of assets to share
***_ Tables, views, volumes, notebooks
***_ ALTER SHARE ADD TABLE / VIEW / SCHEMA
** Adding assets
***_ WITH HISTORY for time travel
***_ AS alias for external naming
***_ ADD SCHEMA for all current+future assets
** D2D Recipient
***_ Requires recipient sharing identifier
***_ SELECT CURRENT_METASTORE()
***_ CREATE RECIPIENT ... USING ID '...'
** Open Recipient
***_ CREATE RECIPIENT (no ID)
***_ DESCRIBE RECIPIENT → activation link
***_ Send link via secure channel (one-time)
** Grant access
***_ GRANT SELECT ON SHARE TO RECIPIENT
***_ REVOKE to remove access
***_ DROP RECIPIENT to delete
@endmindmap
